    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Dragon Gate: Tournament</strong> is a futuristic arcade combat racer for up to four players in which only the fastest and most skillful survive. In fast-paced, short races, you fight for every metre while an orbital laser pulverises anyone who falls too far behind. Knocked out? No problem! With homing missiles, you can still intervene in the action and decide who comes out on top. Are you ready to become the champion?</h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3283730/extras/82fdddb1388f9d9d7f557ee29b328d5e.avif?t=1771860995\" width=600 height=109 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In <i>Dragon Gate: Tournament</i>, up to four players race against each other in multiple high-speed sprints, competing to earn points. A sprint ends when only one player remains, as any player who falls too far behind the leader is eliminated by a powerful enormous orbital beam.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3283730/extras/2cb15b0d303da2dada0b3f2a9eb3cbb8.poster.avif?t=1771860995\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3283730/extras/2cb15b0d303da2dada0b3f2a9eb3cbb8.webm?t=1771860995\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3283730/extras/2cb15b0d303da2dada0b3f2a9eb3cbb8.mp4?t=1771860995\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3283730/extras/4203f74ba629e56a222b9b3ba8e53e5f.avif?t=1771860995\" width=600 height=110 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Upgrade your car with Power-UPs such as a <i>Gatling Gun</i>, <i>Explosive Barrels</i> or a <i>Portal Cannon</i> to give you the advantage you need to outrun your rivals.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3283730/extras/fa272f153c22e43133d540512842febe.poster.avif?t=1771860995\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3283730/extras/fa272f153c22e43133d540512842febe.webm?t=1771860995\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3283730/extras/fa272f153c22e43133d540512842febe.mp4?t=1771860995\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3283730/extras/e4c294b94e9a68ce5646a60fef11002d.avif?t=1771860995\" width=600 height=110 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Even after elimination, players can still influence the outcome by launching homing missiles at the remaining racers, impacting the race and shaping victory or defeat!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3283730/extras/85522fee108205d2577661b0177435a0.poster.avif?t=1771860995\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3283730/extras/85522fee108205d2577661b0177435a0.webm?t=1771860995\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3283730/extras/85522fee108205d2577661b0177435a0.mp4?t=1771860995\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
